## Initialize SDK [![github]({{ githubIcon }})](https://github.com/openai/openai-node)
AITable's chat completion API is compatible with OpenAI's Node.js SDK. You can use our service with the same SDK by simply changing the configuration as follows:


```javascript
const { Configuration, OpenAIApi } = require("openai");
const configuration = new Configuration({
    apiKey: "{{token}}",
    basePath: "{{apiBase}}/fusion/v1/ai/{{aiId}}"
});
```

## Create chat completions

```javascript
const openai = new OpenAIApi(configuration);
const chatCompletion = await openai.createChatCompletion({
  model: "gpt-3.5-turbo",
  messages: [{role: "user", content: "Hello world"}],
});
```

